Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Card & Adventure Video Games: Monster Rancher Explorer Archive (Game Boy Color): Strategy: Level 50
By Y.K. TAN on Sunday, May 30, 2004 - 10:29 pm:

Stage 50

This stage is stupid....too many psirollers. Firstly, just box all the way up and destroy the box that trap you inside. Stand on the metal block on the left while you wait for the psirollers to come in. Lock the place up when two psirollers are in it.

After that, jump all the way down, and claim the key. Box your way up while jumping over the heads of psiroller to come back up, if you died, that's even better, you can go straight up to the door. But either ways, if you make it this far, you can surely enter the door with ease.
